additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Handle and store safely. Keep out of reach of children. Close the bag properly. www.keepcapsfromkids.eu Keep away from eyes. If product gets into eyes rinse thoroughly with water. Do not ingest. If product is ingested then seek medical advice. Keep out of reach of children. Irritant causes serious eye irritation. Causes skin irritation. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. Do not ingest. Contains Subtilisin. May produce an allergic reaction. IF IN EYES: Rinse cautiously with water for several minutes. Remove contact lenses, if present and easy to do. Continue rinsing.
